  <para>
    <command>OOF.Mesh.Boundary_Conditions.Edit</command> replaces one
    <link linkend="RegisteredClass-BC">boundary condition</link> with
    another in the given &mesh;.  All attributes of the boundary
    condition may be changed, even the <link
    linkend="Section-Concepts-Skeleton-Boundary">boundary</link> to
    which it applies.
  </para>
  <para>
    The <varname>name</varname> parameter is the name of the boundary
    condition to be replaced.  The <varname>condition</varname>
    parameter is the boundary condition that replaces it.
  </para>


